### 新功能2：转写结果预览和分享

**设计思路**：转写完成后显示预览对话框，提供复制和分享功能。

文件：`MainActivity.java`

```java
private String lastTranscribeResult = "";  // 类成员变量

private void showTranscribeResult(String jsonResult) {
    try {
        JSONObject obj = new JSONObject(jsonResult);
        String formatted = obj.optString("formatted", obj.optString("text", ""));
        lastTranscribeResult = formatted;

        // 显示在结果区域
        tvResult.setText(formatted);

        // 显示预览/分享按钮
        btnPreviewShare.setVisibility(View.VISIBLE);
    } catch (JSONException e) {
        tvResult.setText(jsonResult);
        lastTranscribeResult = jsonResult;
        btnPreviewShare.setVisibility(View.VISIBLE);
    }
}

// 预览和分享对话框
private void showPreviewShareDialog() {
    AlertDialog.Builder builder = new AlertDialog.Builder(this);
    builder.setTitle("转写结果");

    // 可滚动的文本预览
    ScrollView scrollView = new ScrollView(this);
    TextView tvPreview = new TextView(this);
    tvPreview.setText(lastTranscribeResult);
    tvPreview.setPadding(32, 32, 32, 32);
    tvPreview.setTextIsSelectable(true);
    scrollView.addView(tvPreview);
    builder.setView(scrollView);

    builder.setPositiveButton("分享", (d, w) -> shareText(lastTranscribeResult));
    builder.setNeutralButton("复制", (d, w) -> {
        ClipboardManager cm = (ClipboardManager) getSystemService(CLIPBOARD_SERVICE);
        cm.setPrimaryClip(ClipData.newPlainText("转写结果", lastTranscribeResult));
        Toast.makeText(this, "已复制到剪贴板", Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();
    });
    builder.setNegativeButton("关闭", null);
    builder.show();
}

private void shareText(String text) {
    Intent intent = new Intent(Intent.ACTION_SEND);
    intent.setType("text/plain");
    intent.putExtra(Intent.EXTRA_TEXT, text);
    startActivity(Intent.createChooser(intent, "分享转写结果"));
}
```

在布局 XML 中添加预览/分享按钮：
```xml
<Button
    android:id="@+id/btnPreviewShare"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="wrap_content"
    android:text="预览 / 分享"
    android:visibility="gone" />
```

在 `onCreate()` 中绑定：
```java
Button btnPreviewShare = findViewById(R.id.btnPreviewShare);
btnPreviewShare.setOnClickListener(v -> showPreviewShareDialog());
```

